Welcome to BL3P

  • Experienced Bitcoin companyBL3P is a product of Bitonic, an experienced Bitcoin company founded in 2012. BL3P is available in all European countries.
  • Bank relations & Compliance BL3P is the only bitcoin exchange based in the Netherlands and holds Dutch bank accounts to process euro transactions.
